        </item>
        <item>
            <title>的士司机周街大叫「无微信啊」兼爆粗，网民：疑后车投诉前车藉「无微信」拒载短途客</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/26/taxinowechatpay/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=taxinowechatpay</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/26/taxinowechatpay/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 06:25:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[的士]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1238232</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>的士司机服务态度与是否应该支援电子支付成为近日热门话题。而昨晚网上更爆出一段短片成为热话，影片中司机在街上一个的士站落车不断重复狂叫「无微信啊！」兼狂爆粗口。网民质疑，片中司机藉「无微信」而拒载短途客，将短途客塞向后车，令后车司机不满而口角。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1238233 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024052622016-394x580.jpg" alt="" width="394" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024052622016-394x580.jpg 394w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2024052622016.jpg 611w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 394px" /></p><p>昨晚 Facebook 群组「车 cam L（香港群组）」有网民发布一段短片，影片中司机不断狂叫「无微信啊」引起途人瞩目。影片一开始，看到的士站排第二的后车司机，走向前车司机面前投诉。而前车司机开始发难，在街上狂叫「无微信啊 XX，XXXX，XXX，微信啊无微信丫嘛！无微信啊，无微信丫嘛！无微信啊！XXXX！无微信啊！&#8230;.XXX，无微信点收钱啊，又话我黑的，咁大个牌写住收现金家嘛」。</p><p>影片看到前车司机非常重视其「无微信」的立场，与后方司机在街头口角。网民怀疑，后方司机投诉，是因为前车司机拒载疑似短途客，双方因而口角。而前车司机理直壮以「无微信」为由推掉乘客到后车。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1238239" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240526_2_32_51-694x327.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="327" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240526_2_32_51-694x327.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240526_2_32_51.jpg 798w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>近日网约车、的士服务态度成为热话，政府已经邀请有兴趣人士成立的士车队，希望透过更优质管理，以及能够收取电子支付、能够网约的士，多方面为市民游客提供更好的服务。对于的士是否支援电子支付，市民与司机双方仍然存在分岐，后者认为电子支付需要缴付手续费，相关交易亦会被记录，引入电子支付的司机仍然只占极少数。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyeeyee.lam.104%2Fvideos%2F1360890721272956%2F%3Fidorvanity%3D857985435068408&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=269&amp;t=0" width="269" height="476" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/reel/1360890721272956">车 cam L（香港群组）Facebook 专页</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/12/online-ride-hailing/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">黄凤娴再倡网约车合法化，若的士车队制未能满足市民将再提</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/21/a-14-year-old-is-charged-in-fire-that-destroyed-a-driverless-waymo-vehicle/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">三藩市自动驾驶的士纵火案有进展　14 岁疑犯被起诉</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/10/taxi-team-5/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">的士车队牌照周五起接受申请　最多发 5 牌照 + 车队可自订预订行程收费</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/26/taxinowechatpay/life-tech/epayment/">的士司机周街大叫「无微信啊」兼爆粗，网民：疑后车投诉前车藉「无微信」拒载短途客</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/26/taxinowechatpay/life-tech/epayment/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
